{
    "id": "completionist/award-iii",
    "title": "Forge the Completionist Award III",
    "description": "Build a grand mixed-discipline trophy that celebrates your full v3 journey: printed structure, fine woodworking base, soldered electronics, robotics motion, and a living planter crown.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/completionist_award_iii_forge.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "You did it. Every current v3 quest is complete. Let's celebrate with something worthy: the Completionist Award III, a multi-skill artifact that reflects your whole path so far and points toward where DSPACE can go next.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "print-modules",
                    "text": "I'm ready to build the Award III"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "print-modules",
            "text": "First we fabricate the precision shell pieces: crest, electronics tray, and planter ring. Start here so every later subsystem has proper mounting geometry.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "print-completionist-iii-modules",
                    "text": "3D print Award III modules"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "wood-base",
                    "text": "Printed modules are dimensionally accurate",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "be9cb892-f4b2-45fd-ae2b-34d3190acb59",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "wood-base",
            "text": "Now craft the pine pedestal: square, sanded, and oil-finished. This is the structural anchor and the visual warmth beneath the high-tech layers.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "mill-completionist-iii-wood-base",
                    "text": "Mill and finish the wood base"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "electronics-harness",
                    "text": "Pedestal is flat, sealed, and mount-ready",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "fd54da0d-cf87-4860-bf74-df3be8a95f90",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "electronics-harness",
            "text": "Time to wire the heartbeat: solder the LED ring and control harness, then heat-shrink each joint for long-term durability.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "solder-completionist-iii-harness",
                    "text": "Solder and heat-shrink the harness"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "robotics-integration",
                    "text": "Harness passes continuity and polarity checks",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "37f159f8-e8a2-4721-9608-c4b25855092e",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "robotics-integration",
            "text": "Integrate motion and intelligence: mount a micro servo that slowly rotates the crest while the status LED reflects system health.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "integrate-completionist-iii-robotics",
                    "text": "Install and tune servo subsystem"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "planter-integration",
                    "text": "Servo sweep is smooth and cable-safe",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "e6f5d8eb-1ce2-4a91-b9f4-3bbac465018b",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "planter-integration",
            "text": "Add a living layer: seat the hydroponic micro-planter cup at the top and prime it for herbs. This keeps the trophy connected to growth, not just achievement.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "assemble-completionist-iii-planter",
                    "text": "Install and seed the planter crown"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "final-assembly",
                    "text": "Planter cup is stable and irrigated",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "ba8cc7ec-f6c9-429a-aa7d-4bf8f513f4c9",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "final-assembly",
            "text": "Final assembly and validation: mechanical fit, electrical safety, cable strain relief, and aesthetics. We're building a trophy that can inspire future builders.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "assemble-completionist-award-iii",
                    "text": "Assemble and verify the full Award III"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Award III is complete and fully validated",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "adf69f8d-4b30-4eec-b667-43ff5dfd9892",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "Congratulations. You've proven mastery across systems, craft, debugging, and stewardship. Today this is Award III. Tomorrow? Autonomous farms, orbital fabrication, community labs on every block. Let's keep building that future together.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Claim the Completionist Award III"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
